channel.title: Stripping, and unstripping?
channel.description:
I found two different versions of the 614 server i was looking for, i downloaded both, on the first one, you cannot take off any items, and on the second one, you cant wear anything, so i was thinking i could just rip one from the other, what class or file would i look at to wear stuff.
Basically i need to know what class or file, that allows you to wear items, so i could rip it and add it to my other source, its 614.
